<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8089909>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Novius spp., general appearance of life stages: a. egg laid on Icerya pilosa Green (inset: magnified egg); b, c. larva; d. pupa; e. Novius sexnotatus (Mulsant); f. Novius amabilis (Kapur); g, h. reflex bleeding in Novius amabilis (Kapur)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8089909/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8089913>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Prey of Novius spp. in India: a. Icerya aegyptiaca (Douglas); b, c. Icerya purchasi Maskell; d. Icerya seychellarum (Westwood); e. Icerya pilosa Green; f. Icerya viraktamathi Joshi; g. Labioproctus poleii (Green); h. Hemaspidoproctus cinereus (Green)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8089913/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

